      "description": "First public release.\n\n- Offline HWP/HWPX → PDF (and Markdown) via WebAssembly, no server or API key.\n- PDF modes: image-based (colour + searchable) or text-based (lightweight vector).\n- Markdown extraction with GFM/HTML tables (merged cells supported).\n- Korean/English UI.\n- WASM renderer and font inlined into main.js (single-file install).",
